Lucien Duboscq https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lucien_Duboscq 0 Lucien Duboscq (1893-1935) was a French stage actor. He also starred in two films, including the 1933 drama In Old Alsace.He was a member of the Comédie-Française. Lucien_Duboscq ( 1893-1935 ) was a_French_stage_actor .
